com.google.appinventor.components.runtime.util

Class SdkLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.appinventor.components.runtime.util.SdkLevel

  • public class SdkLevel
extends Object
    Support for discovering which version of the Android SDK is on the phone. For more information about Android API levels see http://developer.android.com/guide/appendix/api-levels.html.
    Author:
    sharon@google.com (Sharon Perl)
